#Realm
Holarctic = Palearctic + Nearctic
Palearctic: Europe + North Asia + North Africa
- Sahara
- Arabia
- Mediterranean
- British Isles
- European Plain
- European Mountains
- Eurasian Steppe
- Japanese Islands
- Tibet
- Manchuria
- Chinese Plain
- Gobi + Taklamakan
- Scandinavia
- Siberia
- Persia
- Central Asia
Nearctic: North America
- Coastal Plain
- Appalachians
- Great Lakes
- Great Plains
- Rocky Mountains
- Canada + Alaska
- Cascadia
- California
- Sonora + Mojave + Chihuahua
Neotropic: Central and South America
- Carribean
- Isthmus: Central America
- Amazonia
- Cerrado
- Andes
- Pampas
- Orinoco
Afrotropic: Sub-Saharan Africa
- Sahel
- Horn of Africa
- African Jungle
- African Savanna
- Madagascar
- Kalahari + Karoo
Indomalaya: South + Southeast Asia
- India
- Indochina
- Philippines
- Java + Sumatra + Borneo
Australasia
- Australia
- New Guinea
- New Zealand
- Wallacea: Sulawesi
Oceania
Antarctica

#Holarctic
mammals: Wolf, Red fox, Brown bear, Red deer, Elk, Lynx

#Palearctic
reptiles: Vipers

#Nearctic
reptiles: Rattlesnakes

#Wallacea
mammals: Anoa (dwarf buffalo), Babirusa
reptiles: Komodo dragon
birds: Maleo

#New Guinea
mammals: Tree-kangaroos, Echidnas, marsupials, mice, bats
birds: Crowned pigeon, Papuan eagle, Cassowary

#Australia
mammals: Platypus, Echidnas, Tasmanian devil, Koala, Kangaroo, marsupials, Dingo, mice, bats
birds: Emu, Cassowary, Lyrebird, Cockatiel, cockatoos, Black swan
reptiles: Taipans, Thorny devil

#New Zealand
birds: Kakapo, Kea, Kiwi
reptiles: Tuatara

#Indomalaya
reptiles: King cobra, Pythons, Dracos

#India
mammals: Blackbuck, Bengal tiger
birds: Peacock

#Afrotropic
mammals: Hippopotamus, African buffalo, Leopard, African elephant, Hyraxes, Aardvark, Honey badger, Cheetah, Warthog
birds: Ostrich, Crowned crane, Secretary bird
reptiles: Chameleons, Mambas, Pythons

#African Savanna
mammals: Lion, Giraffe, Zebra, Rhinoceros, Impala

#African Jungle
mammals: Chimpanze, Gorilla, Okapi
birds: Grey parrot

#Madagascar
mammals: Lemurs, Fossa

#Neotropic
birds: Aras, Toucans
reptiles: Boas
